section_text: 1 1 The provisions of the  Farriers (Registration) Act 1975 specified in the Schedule to this Act shall have effect subject to the amendments set out in the said Schedule. 2 . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .
